        "TileImage": "$($repository 1ea813c8-038d-473a-aecb-ac9afe0adbdb).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47.\r\rYour targets are two armed robbers and a third suspect believed to be assisting their operation. Intelligence indicates the accomplice provided access and information that enabled the operation. The client expects the matter to be handled discreetly, with no trace leading back to the bank.\r\rIntercept the heist, eliminate all three targets, and ensure no witnesses can implicate the bank in the attempted robbery.",
